Package com.chatmotorapi.api

Class MotorDefaultsModels

java.lang.Object
com.chatmotorapi.api.MotorDefaultsModels
public class MotorDefaultsModels
extends Object
Utility class containing default model values for the ChatMotor API. This class provides default values for different types of models used in the API, ensuring a consistent and simplified configuration experience.

Note: This is a utility class and cannot be instantiated.

  • MOTOR_CHAT_MODEL - Default model for chat operations.
  • MOTOR_IMAGE_MODEL - Default model for image generation from text.
  • MOTOR_SPEECH_MODEL - Default model for text-to-speech operations.
  • MOTOR_VISION_MODEL - Default model for vision-related operations.
  • MOTOR_WHISPER_MODEL - Default model for speech-to-text operations.
